
"job"		-> "I am the conjucator and main leader of The Royal Tibians army. We are looking for adventurers to help our legion."
"name"		-> "I am called Tusker. But my real name is Tuskachetes."
"offer"		-> "I have nothing to offer, although, I do have some tasks available and in exchange for completing them, I will reward you nicely."
"trade"		-> *
"buy"		-> *
"sell"		-> *

"tasks"		-> "These are my available tasks Hunters, Dwarves, Ghouls, Goblins, Larvas, Minotaurs all Kind, Rotworms, Orcs all Kind, Scarabs, Trolls, Terror birds, Ancient Scarabs, Apes, Cyclops...",
			   "And Demon Skeleton, Dragon, Dwarf Guard, Dwarf Geomancer, Fire Elemental, Hero, Cyclops Smith, Cyclops Drone, Nightmares, Lizards, Necromancer, Vampire, Behemoth, Dragon Lord, Demon, Hydra, Serpent Spawn, Warlock, Swamp Troll...",
