			   "Crypt Shambler, Black Knight, Mummy, Valkyrie, and Giant Spider."

"easy tasks"	-> "These are my available tasks Hunters, Dwarves, Ghouls, Goblins, Larvas, Minotaurs All Kind, Rotworms, Orcs, Scarabs, Trolls, Swamp Troll, Bug, Hyaena...",
				   "Frost Troll, Wasp, Poison Spider, Witch, Skeleton, Elf Scout, Ghosts, Scorpions, Cave Rat, Rats, Snakes, Lions, Amazon, Valkyrie, and Orc Spearman."
			   
"medium tasks"	-> "These are my available tasks Mummies, Hunter, Tarantulas, Apes, Cyclops, Demon Skeleton, Dwarf Guard, Dwarf Geomancer, Fire Elemental, Lizards, Necromancers, Vampire, Stone Golem, Beholder and Crypt Shamblers."
			   
